> "Everyone in good condition pick up an injured one, Fractil quickly take a
> sample of this... things and all retreat to Black Fortress" Hdyras took
> Cyclonus and helping him move he walked towards the exit coverin his back

Quickly everyone did as was ordered, Fractyl getting a bit of the
frame. As he cut a piece off a surge of energy caused him to drop it
on the ground. he looked at it curiously before he picked it up and
began walking after Hydras and the rest.

Iguanus and inferno also picked up Insecticon and Bruticus-X and began
bringing them back as well.

As they did so Deepstyke could be seen making his way up the tunnel,
followed closely by Phobia and Blackrazor, they all looked ready for
batle.

But when they saw Hydras helping Cyclonus back they slowed and looked
at Cyclonus and then at Hydras, "How is Cyclonus?" Deepstryke said,
genuine concern seeming to be in his voice as he stepped forward to
look at him.

(TAG)

Preston
